data.description: Welcome to this beautifully maintained home in the Winding Creek subdivision. Thoughtfully designed with open concept common living areas while providing individual retreats in the form of 5 bedrooms and 3 baths. There’s also a cozy loft area upstairs that allows separation and entertaining multiple groups of guests. A bedroom and full bath on the main level could be an office or a private sanctuary for your guests. All rooms are generously sized and have ample closet space. Start with the elegant two story foyer and continue past the formal dining room into the kitchen and living room. You will be amazed at the kitchen finishes with stainless appliances and granite countertops. A central island provides seating along with enough room for an informal table/chairs. Beautiful hardwood floors throughout the common areas. Glass doors from the casual dining area open to a covered patio and a large fenced backyard. The patio is large enough to provide seating as well as a grill. Upstairs, the primary bedroom has plenty of windows and natural light. The bathroom is truly   luxurious and the walk-in closet is certainly generous. Three other bedrooms can flex to hold exercise equipment, office space or a game room. Another example of great design in this home is the laundry room. It’s a great use of space and adds extra storage. The community features a pool, playground, sidewalks, fitness area and much more. This summer, welcome your guests with a dip in the pool followed by a BBQ in your private backyard. WELCOME HOME!
